@page "/skills"

<PageTitle>Skills</PageTitle>

<section class="page-header">
    <span class="section-kicker">Skills</span>
    <h1>Growing Technical Strengths</h1>
    <p>
        These skills represent my early but steadily developing toolkit shaped by school projects, labs, and
        self-practice.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="content-grid">
    <div class="tech-card">
        <h2>Programming</h2>
        <ul class="skill-list">
            <li>C# and basic object-oriented programming</li>
            <li>HTML, CSS, and beginner responsive design</li>
            <li>JavaScript fundamentals</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-card">
        <h2>Tools</h2>
        <ul class="skill-list">
            <li>Visual Studio and VS Code</li>
            <li>Git and basic version control workflow</li>
            <li>Figma for simple UI mockups</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-card">
        <h2>Data And Systems</h2>
        <ul class="skill-list">
            <li>SQL basics and table relationships</li>
            <li>Simple form handling and data flow</li>
            <li>Understanding of system planning concepts</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="tech-card">
        <h2>Soft Skills</h2>
        <ul class="skill-list">
            <li>Team collaboration in group activities</li>
            <li>Presentation and communication practice</li>
            <li>Adaptability and willingness to learn</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
